# Code Owners File
# Defines code ownership and review requirements for the Soroban Security Scanner
# Format: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global Owners - All files
*       @protocol-council @security-lead

# Core Protocol & Governance
/GOVERNANCE.md                   @protocol-council @security-lead @technical-lead
/.github/governance/            @protocol-council @technical-lead
/.github/workflows/ci.yml       @devops-team @technical-lead
/.github/workflows/ci-original.yml @devops-team @technical-lead

# Smart Contracts - Highest Security
/contracts/                     @contracts-team @security-lead @protocol-council
/contracts/*.rs                 @contracts-team @security-lead
/contracts/Cargo.toml           @contracts-team @technical-lead

# Core Scanner - High Security
/core-scanner/                  @security-team @technical-lead @protocol-council
/core-scanner/src/              @security-team @technical-lead
/core-scanner/Cargo.toml        @technical-lead @security-lead

# Backend Services
/backend/                       @backend-team @security-lead
/backend/src/                   @backend-team @technical-lead
/backend/Cargo.toml             @backend-team @devops-team

# Frontend Application
/frontend/                      @frontend-team @technical-lead
/frontend/src/                  @frontend-team
/frontend/package.json          @frontend-team @devops-team

# Kubernetes & Infrastructure
/k8s/                           @devops-team @security-lead
/kubernetes/                    @devops-team @security-lead
/deployment/                    @devops-team @security-lead

# Scripts & Automation
/scripts/                       @devops-team @technical-lead
/docker-compose.yml             @devops-team @technical-lead
/docker-compose.llm-patch.yml   @devops-team @technical-lead

# Documentation
/README.md                      @technical-writer @protocol-council
/CONTRIBUTING.md                @technical-writer @protocol-council
/SECURITY.md                    @security-lead @protocol-council

# Configuration Files
/Cargo.toml                     @technical-lead @security-lead
/Cargo.lock                     @technical-lead @security-lead
/stellar-scanner.toml           @technical-lead @security-lead
/.env.example                   @security-lead @devops-team

# Vulnerability & Security Research
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/vulnerability_report.md  @security-lead @protocol-council
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/SECURITY_RESEARCH.md     @security-lead @protocol-council

# Test Files
/tests/                         @quality-team @security-team @technical-lead
/examples/                      @technical-lead @quality-team

# AI/ML Patch Service
/llm-patch-service/             @ai-team @security-lead @technical-lead

# Kernel Modules
/src/                           @kernel-team @security-lead @technical-lead
